name: 1. Grill Gazebo Canopy
description: If you enjoy spending your day in the great outdoors look no further, this charming grill gazebo. This stylish grill gazebo will make the perfect addition to your backyard, pool, or patio area. This terrific gazebo will protect any grill from rain, UV rays, or falling debris like leaves, pine needles or sap. This soft top canopy gazebo will not only protect your grill but make any barbecue the talk of the party.
